cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "AnonShield: Scalable On-Premise Pseudonymization for CSIRT Network Vulnerability Data"
message: >-
  If you use AnonShield in your research, please cite the SBRC 2026 paper
  listed under "preferred-citation" below.
type: software
